Derived code
------------------------------------------------------------------------

src/include/prosperopkg/psxpkg.h is a standalone GPL-3.0-or-later
reference reader authored by seregonwar. It is kept as optional reference
code for this fork and is not currently linked into the CMake native
library or command-line tools.

src/include/prosperopkg/lzn_block.hpp and src/src/lzn_block.cpp are a cleaned,
renamed, GPL-3.0-or-later rework by seregonwar of his earlier block-codec
design. The active version removes the old project-specific naming, drops
mandatory third-party compression backends, and targets LibProsperoPkg's LZN
compression experiments.

legacy/csharp/src/LibProsperoPkg/PFS/Compression/Oodle/ is retained only as
part of the archived C# reference implementation by SvenGDK. That legacy
Kraken/newLZ code appears to have been informed by Powzix's "ooz" project
(<https://github.com/powzix/ooz>), whose public repository does not currently
publish a clear license notice. The active C++ rewrite under src/ must not
copy, translate, or vendor code from that legacy Oodle folder or from ooz
unless a compatible license is confirmed.

Any native Kraken/newLZ implementation added to src/ is expected to be a new
clean-room implementation authored for this fork, validated with independent
fixtures and behavior tests rather than copied source.
